com.gmarciani.gmparser.models.grammar.production

Class Production

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gmarciani.gmparser.models.grammar.production.Production
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Production>

    public class Production
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Production>

    Production model.

    A production is a pair of members: a LHS member, and a RHS member.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Giacomo Marciani
    See Also:
    Grammar, Productions, Member
